race.description: Complete Warehouse Solutions Super Maiden Hcp
race.comment: ZING TO ME (6) nice mare who can shed her Maiden status at start eight after the two slick trials. Not that far away when fifth over this track in trip in the heavy (8) conditions last September. Can sit just off the good speed and launch late. MANUKAU (1) kept fresh and back in trip and grade today. Returned good figures with a tough on-pace second over 1200m at Warwick Farm. Has a fitness edge over most of these and no excuses today. PLUME (4) Blue Point mare from Feather on debut for the Hawkes' stable. Closed off well in her last two trials and ticks plenty of boxes from the low barrier. Hard to hold out. INFANT WARRIOR (10) speared across from the wide gate at latest when a courageous second over this track and trip. At her peak now and goes into the exotics.
